beer.beer_description:
A refreshing, full-flavoured lager, brewed using the finest ingredients. Pure Blonde is brewed with no preservatives to deliver an easy-drinking, ultra low carb beer. Hersbrucker hops add a floral and herbal aroma balancing the light style of the beer.

Pure Blonde is brewed longer to break down more natural sugars than usual, delivering a brew with 80% less carbohydrates than regular beer.

With 50% less calories than wine per mL* and 30% less calories than regular beer, Pure Blonde is loved for its pure, crisp taste.

*50% less calories than wine per ml, based on average calorie content of the leading 100 Wine SKUs in Australia. IRI-Aztec wine data, MAT 31/01/15.

Although we make Pure Blonde with malted barley (which contains Gluten), our brewing process breaks down the Gluten. We have had Pure Blonde tested by professionals and the beer contains around 10 parts per million (10 PPM), which equates to 1mg per 100g. Pure Blonde is low in Gluten, but if you're not 100% sure then please seek professional advice.

items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 125 distinct venues!
One cannot live on dank hops alone. Tone down the bitterness and enjoy some smooth flavor. That's 70 different beers with an IBU of 20 or below. Try 5 more for Level 15!

It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That's 340 check-ins with a photo.  Try 5 more for Level 69!
99 bottles of beer on the wall, 99 bottles of beer. Take one down, pass it around.... That's 165 checkins with the serving style of Bottle. Try 5 more for Level 34!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 80 different Lagers! Try 5 more for Level 17!
